data.description: Welcome to your new home! This move-in ready home features 3 bedrooms and 1.75 baths. You will feel right at home from entry into the spacious living room that leads to the kitchen. One of the standout features of this home is its solar power system which saves you money on energy bills. On top of that, you'll notice fresh interior paint and laminate floors.  Don't miss this fantastic opportunity to own a home!
